{"tid":176984,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主人唔願飲水 有咩解決方法（多圖）","createTime":"2017-03-28T14:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T08:21:42.000Z","uid":65279,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75febc6f1122650e1cb804e2e426157b0885d430","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/215223_58c9826beade50108aa65dea41fba202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F215223_58c9826beade50108aa65dea41fba202.jpg&h=fd684d78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/215223_febc7f891b65c5b574a24992803e12b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F215223_febc7f891b65c5b574a24992803e12b7.jpg&h=38381d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/215224_febc7f891b65c5b574a24992803e12b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F215224_febc7f891b65c5b574a24992803e12b7.jpg&h=cdcde48f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/215333_b4419f85e3834ba70fba3260db2afdad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F215333_b4419f85e3834ba70fba3260db2afdad.jpg&h=566b7e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主人唔飲水攪到好少去廁所 同埋便便一粒粒<br />\n怕主人長期落去會有腎病and便秘 <br />\n請問眾貓奴有無解決方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n令付上ig <br />\nig: wowostagram <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea2f7a34a2ae9e75e3d0bfedce17a04c65d9777","tid":176984,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13960949d1902ddb6a521e5a48a95f9ccb566554","tid":176984,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"用咩水機"},{"pid":"29fe927fb6919145f50ebfd066488b00704c882d","tid":176984,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"係佢面前斟水提佢飲<br />\n<br />\n多啲抱起佢摸住佢講：「飲多啲水對你好好架，你好乖架嘛係咪？」"},{"pid":"1f36575b65578716c86300d0f7e19f16cd1da351","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咩水機</blockquote><br />\n插電 噴泉個種"},{"pid":"952b40e23c01c2b9462ef615a1fcf35f5804edcd","tid":176984,"uid":33972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"我屋企果隻又係咁，之前搞到好大鑊<br />\n而家餵糧會加大量水，要佢飲晒先食到<br />\n每日餵兩次糧，每次會落 100 ml 水佢飲晒先食到"},{"pid":"2c676c0d1701fb705f47334a6e35b5592d1b3d4f","tid":176984,"uid":25408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"用噴泉水機<br />\n我朋友隻貓以前都唔飲換左水機就成日飲"},{"pid":"f090df69c0b1d15a0e072fe542d973dd44d2d930","tid":176984,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"試下流動嘅水"},{"pid":"d9c92d68daaf853ff3e9b9755d291953d2001317","tid":176984,"uid":77533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"餵糧加水試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00651b0b96ad6cdf0fe574ae32b1e124ab5e33f6","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企果隻又係咁，之前搞到好大鑊<br />\n而家餵糧會加大量水，要佢飲晒先食到<br />\n每日餵兩次糧，每次會落 100 ml 水佢飲晒先食到</blockquote><br />\n試過一次 但係太有性格<br />\n絕食左兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05649dadd0a34f803378b87e8a1878c1542b09c0","tid":176984,"uid":35095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"直接餵濕糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓貓通常唔會主動飲水架<br />\n就會飲都唔會夠佢需要既份量<br />\n<br />\n濕糧既話<br />\n就算佢唔飲水都夠水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238d3ce9d18e99401babecdfd6357bdaef37ee8b","tid":176984,"uid":33972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企果隻又係咁，之前搞到好大鑊<br />\n而家餵糧會加大量水，要佢飲晒先食到<br />\n每日餵兩次糧，每次會落 100 ml 水佢飲晒先食到</blockquote><br />\n試過一次 但係太有性格<br />\n絕食左兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開頭我係分 4 5 次咁加，要佢食啲飲啲咁<br />\n之後慣左就一次過加晒 100 ml"},{"pid":"81598264404e354269898e70af6aa6d59517dfa9","tid":176984,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"罐罐濕糧加水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf64d04a6cce95434ec13de72433b71de49ddba1","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>罐罐濕糧加水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放足兩日 行埋糧到都做埋屎個動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0543583bbdd4ef70e727fd166258071c4d047123","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"我試過換蒸餾水 水喉水 煮過嘅水 都唔飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bf50f936472ccf72a9553830f627cfd8d68cf4","tid":176984,"uid":65279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接餵濕糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓貓通常唔會主動飲水架<br />\n就會飲都唔會夠佢需要既份量<br />\n<br />\n濕糧既話<br />\n就算佢唔飲水都夠水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 有呀 但係13蚊一罐 日日開都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa915157aa6c56a46fd25e466a35fb5f400765e","tid":176984,"uid":35095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直接餵濕糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓貓通常唔會主動飲水架<br />\n就會飲都唔會夠佢需要既份量<br />\n<br />\n濕糧既話<br />\n就算佢唔飲水都夠水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 有呀 但係13蚊一罐 日日開都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一餐乾一餐濕啦<br />\n如果佢唔肯飲水，好可能會有泌尿系統問題<br />\n到時用既錢肯定貴過D罐罐<br />\n當一日食$13乾糧<br />\n一個月都係$390，都唔會太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你餵開邊隻罐罐？<br />\n你可買大罐既，一罐分兩餐餵都OK<br />\n另外果半罐雪住佢<br />\n第二日用熱水浸暖之後餵<br />\n<br />\n有D Grain free 既罐罐都係$18-20，例如kakato、instinct、wellness core<br />\n分兩餐就平好多"},{"pid":"c2c2126c8a013b3e2f7c2fc22a208fa31926294c","tid":176984,"uid":4589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"濕糧已經夠水<br />\n唔使溝水開<br />\n飲太多水都唔得"},{"pid":"2ea28ffa044a331caebd53a9aac5b3fde374a691","tid":176984,"uid":57374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f8484d18f42e89a09507dbd5b48b2619f38ca2","tid":176984,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"你個咀吸一啖水 咀對咀餵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b14e82f1929f93fddfe27173f0e4724452d8b1","tid":176984,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"我由主人3 、4個月已經餵罐加水<br />\n習慣左有時玩完都自動走去飲水<br />\n<br />\n少屙尿就算未去到腎病都會尿道生石，嗰度要醫已經一大筆，唔好為左幾廿蚊一日揾隻貓健康搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65e0727ff6738e600377adf0744191647761a0d","tid":176984,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>直接餵濕糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓貓通常唔會主動飲水架<br />\n就會飲都唔會夠佢需要既份量<br />\n<br />\n濕糧既話<br />\n就算佢唔飲水都夠水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 有呀 但係13蚊一罐 日日開都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一餐乾一餐濕啦<br />\n如果佢唔肯飲水，好可能會有泌尿系統問題<br />\n到時用既錢肯定貴過D罐罐<br />\n當一日食$13乾糧<br />\n一個月都係$390，都唔會太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你餵開邊隻罐罐？<br />\n你可買大罐既，一罐分兩餐餵都OK<br />\n另外果半罐雪住佢<br />\n第二日用熱水浸暖之後餵<br />\n<br />\n有D Grain free 既罐罐都係$18-20，例如kakato、instinct、wellness core<br />\n分兩餐就平好多</blockquote><br />\n濕糧再加少少水啦，飲唔夠水搞到泌尿有問題手尾好長<br />\n<br />\n罐頭買applaws啦<br />\n有一排轉左kakato, 因為平d, 但有個朋友買左一罐入面有骨，隻貓差d啃左，好彩最後嘔返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我隻貓成日食濕糧飲雞湯，而家會自己飲水，不過貓砂就用得好快<br />\n<br />\n同埋食濕糧要勤力擦牙，食左一年全濕糧勁多牙石，個口勁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd03441daf86c1226cb1687b977b46ef2348e01a","tid":176984,"uid":90360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人會餵湯包？<br />\n其實好唔好咖？<br />\n因為日日濕糧都真係幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2d40c81600ad5159c64015d4e3fab57a01b775","tid":176984,"uid":29818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"我餵濕糧+一日一餐貓奶"},{"pid":"1ee0c2817de75011a2dffdbe905250d2c0229157","tid":176984,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人會餵湯包？<br />\n其實好唔好咖？<br />\n因為日日濕糧都真係幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨食湯包唔夠飽，過一陣又肚餓<br />\n<br />\n只可以當飲多左水, 當主食仲貴過食罐頭"}]}